Introduction to maven -> 
There are two popular build tools which are used in spring boot 
	1.Maven 
	2.Gradle 
	
	Maven -
		Things maven can do -
			Create New Projects 
			Manage Dependencies and their versions 
			Build Jar 
			Run your application locally like tomcat, jetty etc...
			Run Unit tests 
			Deploy to test environment 
			
			Maven will help you to do all these and more 